{"tid":2020822,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"（高清版本）「地厚天高」登陸iTunes Store","createTime":"2020-05-17T10:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T13:08:35.000Z","uid":62799,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6118936ba241bd29cf34067a001c8909f4beb2e9","tid":2020822,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/269743803520492/posts/971355073359358/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F269743803520492%2Fposts%2F971355073359358%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=4ef1e5a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/269743803520492/posts/971355073359358/?d=n</a> <br />\n<br />\niTunes 直接下載連結：<a href=\"https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Z7WB8p&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=9cb8e370\" target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>經過多月的努力，《地厚天高》終於在50個國家上架 iTunes Store。一直以來，我們聽到不少觀眾的反映，希望能簡易地觀看數位高清版本的《地厚天高》。在家裡沒有DVD機、海外的朋友，機會來了！<br />\n<br />\n按以下鏈結或直接於 iTunes 搜尋「Lost In The Fumes」就可以立即串流觀看《地厚天高》！最後，多謝影意志各合作單位的努力，讓這部紀錄片可以走出香港，讓世界各地的更多朋友得悉香港情況。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Lost in the Fumes&quot; is now available internationally on iTunes Store on more than 50 countries! For all of you who don't have a DVD player or cannot get the DVD locally, you can now watch the documentary in the comfort of your own home with the newly released digital version. <br />\n<br />\nWe would also like to thank our distributor Ying E Chi for all the efforts that made this possible. Click in the following link for purchase or rental:  <a href=\"https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2Z7WB8p&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=9cb8e370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2Z7WB8p</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n#地厚天高 #iTunes #LostInTheFumes<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/698F37q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F698F37q.jpg&h=03f0ca65&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e04c21a0543a9643f7f202c05dc8e0e5b3446fa","tid":2020822,"uid":66260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"希望Netflix都可以有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5af668afeb595009411ba1eff5b611613b4122","tid":2020822,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:08:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尚欠91%！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EQt3hkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEQt3hkf.jpg&h=d8fea6e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌連結</span>：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cMLSEJ&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=20f3c44e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cMLSEJ</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n來源（區議員認證）：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1162995320709549/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F915080692167681%2Fposts%2F1162995320709549%2F&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e61xvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=454c6386\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/915080692167681/posts/1162995320709549/</a><br />\n<br />\n#借位"},{"pid":"6795c63db4b27119413a171dda0743d907f24da5","tid":2020822,"uid":83865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e04c21a0543a9643f7f202c05dc8e0e5b3446fa","tid":2020822,"uid":66260,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:07:02.000Z","msg":"希望Netflix都可以有得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T11:12:28.000Z","msg":"佢加埋之峰係net